Q&A
What is Pundi X InStore QR Code Crypto Payment?
QR Code Crypto Payment is a method of making payments using cryptocurrency by scanning a QR code provided by a verified Pundi X merchant. This allows customers to pay for their purchases with cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin, Ethereum, BNB, USDT, and others directly from their own crypto wallets.
How to make Pundi X InStore QR code available in my store?
1. Register a Pundi X merchant account2. Create a “Store”3. Go to InStore QR code and click “Create”4. Download the QR and put it InStore or share it with your customers to pay
How does the customer make an InStore QR Code Crypto Payment?
To make a QR Code Crypto Payment, follow these steps:1. At the checkout, the customer informs the staff to pay crypto2. The staff will show a QR code on a display.3. Customer opens the camera or QR code scanner app on the smartphone.4. Scan the QR code.5. On the customer's phone, input the payment amount in fiat, and choose the preferred cryptocurrency, blockchain, and wallet app to pay.6. Customer confirms the payment on the s crypto wallet before the expiration time.7. Wait for the block confirmation. The customer can enter the email address for the receipt.
Which cryptocurrencies are accepted?
We currently accept Bitcoin (BTC) mainnet, Ethereum (ERC20), BNB (BEP20), PAXG (ERC20), and USDT (ERC20, BEP20, TRC20, Solana). Please check the list in the payment menu for the most up-to-date information.
Is there a minimum or maximum amount for crypto payments?
There may be minimum and maximum transaction limits depending on the cryptocurrency used and the current exchange rates. Please consult with the staff.
Are there any fees for using crypto payments?
Transaction fees may apply and are determined by the blockchain network. These fees will be displayed in your wallet app before the customer confirms the payment.
How long does it take for a crypto payment to be processed?
Most crypto payments are processed within a few minutes. However, transaction times can vary depending on the cryptocurrency network's current activity.
Is QR Code Crypto Payment secure?
Yes, QR Code Crypto Payment is secure. Transactions are encrypted and processed on the blockchain, providing a high level of security and transparency.
Can the customers get a refund if they paid with cryptocurrency?
Refunds for cryptocurrency payments will be processed according to the local franchisee’s refund policy. Please consult your local representative on this.
What if I encounter an issue with InStore QR payment?
If you experience any issues with InStore payment, please contact your local representative for assistance.
Do the customers need a specific wallet app to use QR Code Crypto Payment?
The customers can use any crypto wallet app that supports the cryptocurrencies Pundi X accepts. Popular options include Binance Pay, and any wallet supporting Wallet Connect, ex. MetaMask, Trust Wallet, f(x)Wallet, and more.
